{"id": "1248787579202175030", "channel_id": "1248787579202175030", "type": 0, "author_id": "1189543077648531506", "author_name": "lindongxieyang", "author_bot": false, "content": "想问问有可能复刻吗，有的没拿到实在是有点可惜( p′︵‵。)，还是希望未来考虑复刻一下以前的头像和表情包", "timestamp": "2024-06-07T23:56:00.233000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1248787579202175030", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "课题头像和表情包", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1248566437518381108", "channel_id": "1248566437518381108", "type": 0, "author_id": "818887666908135427", "author_name": "shensizhitiancai", "author_bot": false, "content": "主要还是问在活动结束后，活动页面的入口关了后哪里还能进去？之前有写日常需要好感10才能解就表示活动完了应该也有办法进去吧！可是现在就是找不到入口.....\n有谁能指点下.......", "timestamp": "2024-06-07T09:17:15.947000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1248566437518381108", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」关于繁衍狂热", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1181168103141416960"]}
